{"tid":2122687,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"病毒後遺症 - 蔣芸","createTime":"2020-07-24T06:41:56.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-24T20:42:53.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"0aecfc0d66ec711f0af3f32493aaef71dba74c04","tid":2122687,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T06:41:56.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E8%94%A3%E8%8A%B8/daily/article/20200724/20962007/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E8%2594%25A3%25E8%258A%25B8%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20200724%2F20962007%2F&d=7JJHJI7m8dwGfBTVwC1i6CBot4r0pQQ4M2eut5PfJzM%3D&h=64681085\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E8%2594%25A3%25E8%258A%25B8%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20200724%2F20962007%2F&h=9ec0b57c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E8%94%A3%E8%8A%B8/daily/article/20200724/20962007/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n病毒後遺症 - 蔣芸<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple_sub/20200724/large/1595486898_3c3f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple_sub%2F20200724%2Flarge%2F1595486898_3c3f.jpg&h=ef20adf0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n最近才聽到的一個新名詞，是另一種疾病的名字曰夫源病，不錯它的來源是新冠肺炎，也就是因疫情而來的後遺症；。。。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n一般而言女人老了反而大氣了，不再計較了，而男人老了則變小器了，不僅指花錢消費用度方面的精打細算，而是對女人操作家務事如孔夫子進大廟每事問每事批評且眼高手低，令人不勝其煩，不少女人有同感於如今疫情嚴重，上班族閒在家，放着公事不幹，多出了太多時間，用來監控指導一向是家中主人的主婦，這樣的轉變不產生矛盾才怪。<br />\n<br />\n疫情的後遺症不免多了新興的怨偶，夫婦為雞毛蒜皮而結下樑子，愈結愈多愈深，一旦爆發起來，雙方都認為這種日子若是可忍孰不可忍。<br />\n<br />\n多少年的相處感情，有時也敵不過日常生活日積月累下來的不滿，不由得不講吓日本女人，年輕時受盡大男子丈夫之氣，忍到了年老倒成為日本女人報復的最好時機，如今日本虐夫之現況已時有所聞吧。 <br />\n<br />\n蔣芸<br />\n電郵 :mcwriter@appledaily.com"},{"pid":"1cf3bb80850c126521cc91878ed5d2bed61b9c90","tid":2122687,"uid":431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T20:42:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}